00:01:30.560 --> 00:01:33.560
Oh, I planted them down my gran's back.

00:01:33.560 --> 00:01:35.560
Ha!

00:01:35.560 --> 00:01:39.560
This is not a reference to some senior citizens or manomy folks,

00:01:39.560 --> 00:01:42.160
it means that he's talking about in the backyard,

00:01:42.160 --> 00:01:44.160
but this is the kind of language they have.

00:01:44.160 --> 00:01:48.960
God knows what happens when the local council comes and digs up gran's front.

00:01:48.960 --> 00:01:50.960
Ha!

00:01:53.760 --> 00:01:55.760
There is...

