There's also, you know, in the...

00:01:57.760 --> 00:02:00.760
There's a lovely...

00:02:00.760 --> 00:02:04.760
The language has got some lovely Welsh words in it.

00:02:04.760 --> 00:02:08.760
I wonder how many of you here remember the word, kuch?

00:02:08.760 --> 00:02:10.760
Kuch.

00:02:10.760 --> 00:02:16.760
Kuch in Wales, in South Wales particularly, has four delightful meanings,

00:02:16.760 --> 00:02:20.760
as John Edwards goes to some pains to explain in his tape.

00:02:20.760 --> 00:02:22.760
He says, kuch under...

00:02:22.760 --> 00:02:25.760
Kuch, do you remember the kuch under the star?

00:02:25.760 --> 00:02:27.760
Where you used to store stuff?

00:02:27.760 --> 00:02:30.760
There's a lot of heads, not in a way, folks.

00:02:30.760 --> 00:02:34.760
There's the kuch it away, keep it safe.

00:02:34.760 --> 00:02:38.760
I used to say to the dog, remember, she was a faithful dog, kuch!

00:02:38.760 --> 00:02:40.760
And the dog would come to heel.

00:02:40.760 --> 00:02:44.760
But you know, the most beautiful kuch of all

00:02:44.760 --> 00:02:47.760
was when you used to kuch up to your man.

00:02:47.760 --> 00:02:50.760
Back in Wales, if you thought you were going to love folks,

00:02:50.760 --> 00:02:52.760
you don't know what you've missed.

00:02:53.760 --> 00:02:56.760
In Wales, traditionally, I remember as a child,

00:02:56.760 --> 00:02:59.760
whenever I used to fall and graze my knees,

00:02:59.760 --> 00:03:01.760
I used to come and kuch up to me gran.

00:03:01.760 --> 00:03:06.760
And kuching up to my gran meant you'd put in a shawl

00:03:06.760 --> 00:03:09.760
and wrapped around, and there you were.

00:03:09.760 --> 00:03:12.760
Away from the world's worries and cares,

00:03:12.760 --> 00:03:14.760
there you were, kuched up to your gran.

00:03:14.760 --> 00:03:16.760
Isn't that marvelous, wasn't it, eh?

00:03:16.760 --> 00:03:19.760
That's why we've always grown up with a smile on our face.

00:03:19.760 --> 00:03:22.760
I must admit, when I got on into little life,

00:03:22.760 --> 00:03:25.760
I learned that you could kuch at other things too.

